channel.title: Hybrid PvP Dupes
channel.description:
I've fixed one dupe, the one where you trade, accept, and run away, some guy made a video showing it if you don't know what it is: [youtube]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2P-VT-c4za0[/youtube]
Please do me a favor and list all the known dupes in Hybrid PvP v3. Even if you don't have a fix for it. I will try to fix it, and if I do, I'll make a tutorial or snippet.
